channel.title: In need of RicScape v3 source
channel.description:
Hi everyone, i am trying to find RicScape v3 source. Not RichScape nor RickScape, its ricscape. :P
It is one with many commands and an amazing server pking, training,...
I couldn`t find any which fits me, most of them are HIGLY ( to the sky and over ) edited, with almost every single thing changed,... . :(
If you could help me i would really appreciate. :D
Thanks, Br.
